        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued May 6 at 6:19PM CDT by NWS Lubbock TX</headline>
        <description>At 619 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Idalou, or 15 miles north of Slaton, moving east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Nickel size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Idalou, Ralls, Lorenzo, and Cone.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
